# Internal/operator Meta-Layer project data — regenerated fresh from Drive (META_DATA_ROOT) at
# build time by scripts/build-card-data.js. Repo is public: a git-tracked copy is fetchable via
# raw.githubusercontent.com regardless of the deploy-time public trim (scripts/deploy-public-trim.mjs),
# so these must never be committed. Only card-data.json (the single allowlisted-partner summary)
# is intentionally public and stays tracked — cards-*.json covers EVERY project (including
# non-allowlisted ones), not just the one deploy-public-trim.mjs actually serves, so it is
# internal-by-default here too: PUBLIC_PARTNER_IDS in deploy-public-trim.mjs is what decides which
# single cards-<id>.json actually reaches the live public site, regenerated fresh at build time.
/public/registry.json
/public/operator-*.json
/public/sorular-*.json
/public/strateji-*.json
/public/cards-*.json
partner-inbox/baris.md
